{"id": 1964, "genre": 1001, "title": "你遭遇过哪些意外的小型财务问题？", "description": "买定期理财产品的时候多打了个 0，于是资金链直接崩掉了。（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 1566, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20171018104109W09LlxszAH836oEX.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-10-20T03:00:45Z", "options": [{"id": 243211, "content": "花呗临时额度………", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 235507}, {"id": 243473, "content": "发红包。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1088651}, {"id": 243226, "content": "\n\n在国外画廊吴修的作品价格标价不菲，2016年国内作品价格，5万/平尺左右。坊间有许多书法家临摹他的泼墨作品。\n2011年吴修先生早年友赠德国朋友一幅泼墨作品《鹰》在丹麦商界酒会被丹麦商界人士竟拍168万收藏而一夜成名，名扬中外艺术圈。\n", "image": "img/option/option/20171022135604Zwd14LKeC8t7UFuk", "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1164270}, {"id": 243739, "content": "不发工资", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1159127}, {"id": 243740, "content": "支付宝被冷冻", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1159127}, {"id": 243229, "content": "拖欠工资、各种鸡汤安慰。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 969608}, {"id": 243231, "content": "长期缺钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1226893}, {"id": 246048, "content": "去迪士尼没带现金", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1174239}, {"id": 244264, "content": "报名了某英语学习机构，后因其他情况要退学，去上课连一周都没有的我，退学费被拖延了一个月，并扣了五六千", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1153905}, {"id": 243241, "content": "国庆长假随了大把的份子钱，现在天气越来越冷了，只想存点钱给自己买条秋裤。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 795837}, {"id": 257581, "content": "对蚂蚁财富的定期收益上瘾，买买买结果失算没钱交房租。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1075906}, {"id": 243505, "content": "借钱没还", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1165641}, {"id": 243511, "content": "身怀一元坐不起公交", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1104691}, {"id": 243772, "content": "吃饭时微信支付bug，身上没带现金，没下支付宝?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1165795}, {"id": 243025, "content": "在中国最南方的城市工作，国庆回了趟位于中国最北方的家，并参加了两场婚礼。", "image": null, "praise_count": 211, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 829201}, {"id": 243281, "content": "十月份掏出了两个月工资的分子，工资不涨，分子涨??", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 674282}, {"id": 243026, "content": "毕业工作时旅游花呗白条剁手太多，还款才发现，咦我的钱呢？", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1013083}, {"id": 243027, "content": "突然一大波婚礼来袭，还想着去参加，日子顿时过的紧巴巴。", "image": null, "praise_count": 50, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 607970}, {"id": 243028, "content": "拖欠工资?", "image": null, "praise_count": 66, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 454115}, {"id": 243030, "content": "房租押一付三?", "image": null, "praise_count": 177, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1216775}, {"id": 243031, "content": "买了活期理财，晚上8点提现发现第二天到账", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 153801}, {"id": 243032, "content": "试用期这段时间…不过结个婚，钱又回来了", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 928677}, {"id": 243034, "content": "去老饭馆没带现金", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1030268}, {"id": 243036, "content": "法官和流氓合伙抢钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1022071}, {"id": 243038, "content": "学生党生不大不小的病", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1157650}, {"id": 243044, "content": "跟市场消息，全仓买入，正好被收割", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 814778}, {"id": 243045, "content": "亚马逊出了新的kindle oasis（已经开始吃土", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 294836}, {"id": 246117, "content": "房贷压力大?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1107980}, {"id": 243046, "content": "信用卡花呗刷刷刷，下个月还钱时傻眼了……", "image": null, "praise_count": 90, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 255265}, {"id": 243049, "content": "取钱的时候突然发现只有99.8了", "image": null, "praise_count": 52, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 181495}, {"id": 243051, "content": "想辞职，不好找更高工资的工作，还背着房贷", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 258066}, {"id": 243052, "content": "实习生扣税制度", "image": null, "praise_count": 49, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 441858}, {"id": 243053, "content": "和女友去宾馆钱不够", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 986592}, {"id": 243821, "content": "存款都买理财了，信用卡还款日发现无法还款且理财不能立即赎回。还被信用卡中心按照逾期罚款。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1143922}, {"id": 243054, "content": "用了信用卡取现 被男朋友骂怎么不找我借钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 651076}, {"id": 243055, "content": "突然需要动手术", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147506}, {"id": 243056, "content": "9月份工资给了国庆，10月份工资给了双11，11月工资给了双12，12月工资给了元旦，元旦工资给了过年，2月份工资给了三八妇女节，3月份工资给了清明踏青，4月份工资给了五一，5月份工资给了端午......", "image": null, "praise_count": 297, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1125902}, {"id": 243057, "content": "关系很好的亲戚家小孩出生，平时买对银耳钉都再三思考的我，送起了金子。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1097506}, {"id": 243058, "content": "在贫穷的状态下借钱给了更贫穷的朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 92, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 162821}, {"id": 243060, "content": "去年北京房市930政策，一夜间多出的那些首付啊~", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 410813}, {"id": 243061, "content": "装修中期验收，发现水电改造加吊顶施工的钱超过了银行可用余额……", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 110288}, {"id": 243062, "content": "投了一点闲钱炒股，结果股灾了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1007288}, {"id": 243065, "content": "花呗欠了几个零", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 783916}, {"id": 243066, "content": "看演唱会，买了最贵的票。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 911827}, {"id": 243067, "content": "没有遇到过…各种信用卡花呗微粒贷金条杂七杂八能让我应对现阶段遇到的任何难题～", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 687093}, {"id": 242301, "content": "辞职gap一小段时间，医保刚停掉的时候生病了", "image": null, "praise_count": 94, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 242302, "content": "发工资前出差两周，垫付了高额酒店费", "image": null, "praise_count": 40, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 243075, "content": "上了大学之后感觉淘宝是我家，生活费不够花", "image": "img/option/option/20171020151344wm4yPx1B0osVR2Qb.jpg", "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1162419}, {"id": 243077, "content": "发工资日即是信用卡还款日，然而工资没准时发！", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1160431}, {"id": 243846, "content": "现在不就是么，一如既往的贫穷，没追求。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1166766}]}